Quotes on addressing wage arrears for migrant workers from Qian Xueming
2012-03-10 08:19:19 GMT
BEIJING, March 10 (Xinhua) -- Following are some quotes on addressing wage delays for migrant workers from Qian Xueming, a political advisor from the China Democratic National Construction Association, at the annual session of the Chinese People's Political Consultative Conference National Committee:-- Measures should be taken resolutely to address wage arrears for migrant workers.-- The monthly payment system should be strictly carried out.-- A system of "wage delayed, projects suspended" should be implemented in the construction industry.
